@startuml
title Builder - Ejemplo 3 - solucion para datos de prueba
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class TestUserBuilder {
    +named(String name): TestUserBuilder
    +asAdmin(): TestUserBuilder
    +inactive(): TestUserBuilder
    +build(): User
  }
  class User {
    +toString(): String
  }
}

TestUserBuilder ..> User : crea
Main ..> TestUserBuilder : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
